BEGIN_PGML

Divide. Make sure your answer is reduced to lowest terms.

 [`` \frac{\frac{[$a]}{[$b]}}{[$c]}= ``]

 Answer: [_______________]{$ans} [@ AnswerFormatHelp("numeric") @]*


